name: Auto-Generate Cinematic Animal Videos & Sound from Form using Dumpling AI

parameters.content:
### üü® Sticky Notes for Workflow: Create Cinematic Animal Videos & Audio

üü° **Trigger: Form Submission**  
Starts when a user fills out a form with a title, 4 animals, and a visual style.

üü° **Format Inputs**  
Prepares animal inputs as an array and pulls the selected style for processing.

üü° **Generate Cinematic Prompts (OpenAI)**  
Each animal is transformed into a cinematic, first-person prompt using GPT-4.

üü° **Create AI Image (Dumpling AI)**  
Each prompt is sent to Dumpling AI to generate a high-quality AI image.

üü° **Motion Prompt for Video (OpenAI)**  
The image prompt is rewritten into a motion video prompt with natural movements.

üü° **Generate Motion Video (Leonardo)**  
Leonardo AI turns each image into a short animated video clip using the motion prompt.

üü° **Generate Audio Prompt (OpenAI)**  
GPT-4 generates a vivid sound prompt based on the style.

üü° **Create Ambient Sound (ElevenLabs)**  
The sound prompt is used to generate a 20-second ambient audio file.

üü° **Upload Audio to Drive**  
The generated .mp3 is saved to a Google Drive folder and made shareable.

üü° **Merge Videos and Audio (Creatomate)**  
All videos and audio are stitched into a single cinematic video with text overlays.

üü° **Upload Final Video**  
The completed video is uploaded to Google Drive in the ‚ÄúAI generated Videos‚Äù folder.

üü° **Log Output to Sheet**  
Video title and share link are logged into Google Sheets for future access.

values.content:
=Task:
You are an advanced AI that transforms a country name or an animal into a vivid, cinematic prompt meant for image generation only. The visual should depict a powerful, mythical warrior with the head of a symbolic animal, walking slowly and majestically toward the viewer. The scene must reflect the cultural essence of the country or the natural environment of the animal.

Rules for Output Generation:

Focus on front-facing, full-body motion in a slow, majestic walk

The warrior should be muscular, highly detailed, and visually dominant

Add motion details like cape flow, weapon movement, foot pressure

For country input: use accurate terrain, architecture, weather, and mood

For animal input: use the animal‚Äôs natural habitat as the setting

Background must be slightly blurred for cinematic depth

Output must be in plain text, no JSON

Keep each output below 950 characters

Do not generate video prompts

üîª Input Format Examples:
makefile
Copy
Edit
Input: Morocco, Brazil, Japan, Nigeria  
Input: Tiger, Eagle, Gorilla, Falcon

üîª Output Format Example :
Input: Morocco
Walking with slow, thunderous steps across an ancient desert courtyard, a lion-headed warrior with golden fur and scarred bronze armor moves toward the viewer. His black cape ripples in the hot wind, dust kicking around his armored sandals. Muscles flex under leather carved with Berber motifs, and a curved blade glints at his hip. Behind him, the blurred kasbah walls glow under orange sunlight, casting long shadows across the tiled ground.
It is is very important to note that the prompt must not exceed 950 characters

values.content:
=You are helping me generate a motion video prompt based on a previous image generation prompt.

I will provide the image prompt, and your job is to rewrite it so it can be used to create a motion video using Leonardo.ai.

Your output must follow these rules:

Keep the subject, style, and atmosphere from the original image prompt

Add natural motion elements (such as camera pan, slow zoom, blinking, fog moving, flickering lights, etc)

Write in a descriptive cinematic tone

Keep the response short, between 1 to 2 sentences

Return only the rewritten motion prompt as plain text

Ensure the output includes a line break at the end

Example input:
"A black cat sitting on a haunted piano in a dark room, ghostly ambiance, cinematic style"

Example output:
"A black cat blinking slowly as ghostly light flickers across the haunted piano, the camera pans slowly, cinematic mood"
=Now, generate a motion video prompt from this image prompt:{{ $(' Clean: Remove Line Breaks from Prompt').item.json.prompt }}

values.content:
=# Overview
You are a master sound prompt generator. Given a style, generate a vivid one-to-two sentence prompt that describes the ambiance, tone, and key sound elements to create an immersive audio scene. Use evocative language to capture the essence of the style.

## Example
- Style: Haunted Ghost Hunters
- Output: Eerie whispers echo through a decaying mansion as floorboards creak under cautious footsteps. A distant, distorted radio crackles with ghostly voices, while a cold wind howls through shattered windows.

input.prompt: A samurai warrior with the head of a regal white crane strides through a misty sakura grove, cherry petals drifting in the breeze and pressing into the mossy earth beneath his deliberate steps; his indigo cape and engraved armor move subtly with the wind, while the camera slowly tracks his approach, catching the gentle swing of his katana as morning light glints across blade and drifting fog, with torii gates and pagoda rooftops fading in and out of focus in the tranquil mist.

The crowned eagle-headed warrior strides powerfully through swirling dawn mist on the vibrant savannah, his ornate cloak billowing and dust churning beneath each step, while the camera slowly zooms in as warm sunlight flickers across rising ancient Benin bronze plaques and shifting shadows of acacia trees.

A bear-headed warrior strides powerfully through a snow-laden, windswept plain, icy breath curling as fur and cloak ripple in the harsh wind, armor glinting with each step; flurries of snow swirl up with every heavy footfall while the camera slowly tracks his advance, onion domes and dark pine forests shifting in the drifting wintry haze behind him.

The jackal-headed warrior strides forward through swirling sands, muscles rippling as his obsidian skin gleams, cape and gold sashes billowing in the wind; the camera follows with a slow cinematic pan while heat shimmers over blurred pyramids and ancient obelisks beneath a blazing, dusk-lit sky.
